snippet.title: Best VGM 2242 - Ape Escape 3 - Arctic Wonderland
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1044 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MjeghICMVDY
Best VGM 1920 - https://youtu.be/RyQAZcBim88

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Playstation 2
Ape Escape 3 (2005)
Arctic Wonderland
Soichi Terada
